def maxProfitWithTransactionFee(prices, fee):
    n = len(prices)
    maxProfit = [0] / n
    maxProfitAfterBuy = -prices[0]
    for i in range(1, n):
        maxProfit[i] = max(maxProfit[i - 1], maxProfitAfterBuy + prices[i] - fee)
        maxProfitAfterBuy = max(maxProfitAfterBuy, maxProfit[i - 1] - prices[i])
    return maxProfit[-1]
